<p>The CURRENT SESSIONS is a contemporary dance series which showcases works from emerging choreographers that are expanding the genre. We are interested in producing works that are fresh, raw, experimental and curious; we want to provide our audience with a glimpse of what dance is right now, and what the future generation of dancemakers has to offer.</p>
<p>Third time\'s a charm with three great shows packed with raw talent, sweetness and curiosity. Come to one of our programs and take a peek at our movement, or join in on the Sunday fun and take advantage of our Double Feature Deal (both Sunday shows, and witness of ALL choreographers/works, are yours only for $25!!). Don\'t miss out on a weekend filled with some of NYC\'s finest in the contemporary dance scene!</p>
<p>MORE INFORMATION: <br/>
